            <img src="images/logo2.PNG" alt="logo" class="img_logo">
        </div>
        <div class="card-center-footer">
            <p>Made with <img src="images/love.png" class="img_social_media"> By <img src="./img/low-res-logo (1).png" class="img_logo2"> Av. Domingos Odália Filho, 301 - Centro, Osasco - SP, 06010-067</p>
